OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FRape victims to get chance 
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fto meet their abusers      
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, For the first time in Scotland, victims
OL,6, of rape and domestic abuse will be able
OL,7, to formally meet those who harmed them.
OL,9,FIn a process called restorative        
OL,10,Fjustice, victims of murder, sexual     
OL,11,Fabuse and assault can ask for a        
OL,12,Fface-to-face meeting with those        
OL,13,Fconvicted.                             
OL,15,FMinisters plan to make it "widely      
OL,16,Favailable" across the country by the   
OL,17,Fend of this year.                      
OL,19,FSome women's support groups are        
OL,20,Fconcerned it could re-traumatise       
OL,21,Fvictims.                               
